videos.headline: Harden goes to the locker room with apparent leg injury

videos.description: P.J. Tucker picks Kevin Durant's pocket for the steal and races down court to connect with Giannis Antetokounmpo on an exciting alley-oop dunk on the break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tucker rips KD, lobs to Giannis for the slam) 2021/06/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tucker rips KD, lobs to Giannis for the slam

videos.description: Kyrie Irving gets by his man and throws a slick pass between defenders to Bruce Brown for an easy two-handed stuff inside.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie drops a dime to Brown for a thunderous dunk) 2021/06/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie drops a dime to Brown for a thunderous dunk

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo gets the pass and flies right by Kyrie Irving to throw down a dunk with reckless abandon in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis soars over Kyrie for the slam) 2021/06/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis soars over Kyrie for the slam

videos.description: Kyrie Irving flips a pass over his head to a trailing Kevin Durant who glides to the basket to throw down a dunk to get the Barclays crowd out of their seats.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie hooks up with KD for electrifying fast-break slam) 2021/06/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie hooks up with KD for electrifying fast-break slam

videos.description: Blake Griffin cuts to the basket and Kevin Durant finds him with a nice pass for the easy left-handed dunk in the lane for the Nets.
